<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" xmlns:html="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idaafb1bd8-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5" identifier="/us/usc/t10/s7629"><num value="7629">§ 7629.</num><heading> Proceeds: disposition</heading>
<chapeau style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The proceeds of sales of the following shall be paid into the Treasury to the credit of the appropriation out of which they were purchased, and are available for the purposes of that appropriation:</chapeau><paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="idaafb1bd9-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5" identifier="/us/usc/t10/s7629/1"><num value="1">(1)</num><content> Exterior articles of uniform sold under <ref href="/us/usc/t10/s7621">section 7621 of this title</ref>.</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="idaafb1bda-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5" identifier="/us/usc/t10/s7629/2"><num value="2">(2)</num><content> Supplies and military publications sold to educational institutions under <ref href="/us/usc/t10/s7627">section 7627 of this title</ref>.</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="idaafb1bdb-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5" identifier="/us/usc/t10/s7629/3"><num value="3">(3)</num><content> Fuel, oil, other supplies, and services for aircraft of a foreign military or air attache sold under <ref href="/us/usc/t10/s7626">section 7626 of this title</ref>.</content>
</paragraph>
<sourceCredit id="idaafb1bdc-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5">(<ref href="/us/act/1956-08-10/ch1041">Aug. 10, 1956, ch. 1041</ref>, <ref href="/us/stat/70A/260">70A Stat. 260</ref>, § 4629; renumbered § 7629 and amended <ref href="/us/pl/115/232/dA/tVIII">Pub. L. 115–232, div. A, title VIII</ref>, §§ 808(d), 809(a), <date date="2018-08-13">Aug. 13, 2018</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/132/1839">132 Stat. 1839</ref>, 1840.)</sourceCredit>
